{"id":"hokkaido-indicator-catalog-safety-security","municipality_key":"hokkaido-prefecture","policy_field_id":"policy-field-hokkaido-safety-security","source_id":"policy-source-hokkaido-indicators-safety-security","source_document_url":"https://www.pref.hokkaido.lg.jp/fs/1/0/6/4/6/3/2/4/_/12%20%E5%AE%89%E5%85%A8%E3%83%BB%E5%AE%89%E5%BF%830708.pdf","indicator_number_start":74,"indicator_number_end":79,"items":[{"id":"policy-indicator-hokkaido-74","indicator_number":74,"indicator_name_original":"刑法犯認知件数","policy_direction_id":"policy-direction-hokkaido-opportunity-safety","policy_field_ids":["policy-field-hokkaido-safety-security"],"policy_orientation_original":"命とくらしを守る安全・安心な社会の形成","indicator_explanation_original":"警察が発生を認知した刑法犯の件数（暦年実績）。","source_page":1,"series":[{"label":null,"unit_original":"件","temporal_scope":"calendar_year","values":[{"role":"current","period":"2023年","value":22232,"status":"numeric","operator":"exact","aggregation_scope":"single_period","value_text_original":"22,232"},{"role":"intermediate_target","period":"2028年","value":22232,"status":"numeric","operator":"at_most","aggregation_scope":"single_period","value_text_original":"22,232以下かつ過去５年平均値以下"},{"role":"final_target","period":"2033年","value":null,"status":"conditional","aggregation_scope":"single_period","value_text_original":"中間目標値以下かつ過去５年平均値以下"}]}],"target_setting_status":"set","target_setting_rationale_original":"刑法犯認知件数は経済社会情勢により毎年変動するため、認知件数の減少を目指し、固定閾値と過去5年平均値を組み合わせた条件を目標とする。","comparability_note_original":"中間目標は22,232件以下であることに加えて過去5年平均値以下であることも必要な複合条件。最終目標は中間目標値と将来の過去5年平均値に連動するため固定数値へ変換しない。全国の過去推移は参考データとしてKPI系列から除外する。","actual_linkage_status":"not_linked","evaluation_status":"not_assessed","review_status":"reviewed","confidence":"high"},{"id":"policy-indicator-hokkaido-75","indicator_number":75,"indicator_name_original":"重要犯罪の検挙率","policy_direction_id":"policy-direction-hokkaido-opportunity-safety","policy_field_ids":["policy-field-hokkaido-safety-security"],"policy_orientation_origi